Get ready to hop in a time machine to 2006, WoW fans: Blizzard announced that they are bringing back the original so thousands of gamers can relive the most depressing era of their lives.The company has spent the past two years recreating the “Vanilla” version of the game before any expansions were released, so players can finally re-experience that grim period when they suffered from a crippling, all-consuming addiction to the fantasy MMORPG.